					<h3><i class="fa fa-cog fa-spin"></i> This Website <i class="fa fa-cog fa-spin"></i></h3>
					<p>This is the personal website of Peter Davy. It is where I blog about issues that I care about and where I store photos and programs and experiment with computer stuff. I built this website myself so I am responsible for all the content.</p>
						<br>
					<p>At the moment this website is still under construction so I'm not sure yet how it is going to end up. It started out as an exercise in teaching myself how to build a unix server and ended up as my personal website.</p>
					<br>
					<p>The website runs on a VPS (Virtual Private Server) that I built up myself using the software listed on the right. Apart from Ubuntu I had to learn everything else from scratch because I'd never heard of any of it. </p>
